### Options
- `backfill <colour>` — background fill colour.
- `sort <name|rname|size|rsize|time|rtime>` — sort order (default rtime).
- `saving` — used for saving; hide autosave; only in-game.
- `spacing <value>` — pixel spacing around each save image.

